Realtime bottom temperatures from fishing vessels in the past month

  • Checkmark icons denotes latest reports color-coded by vessel.
  • Numbered icons denote multiple reports in that area color-coded by density of reports.
  • Starred icons denote actual reports posted within 10 miles of actual position.
  • Starred icons denote actual reports there have detailed graph, ok-sign icon denote there have not detailed graph.
  • Layer symbol in upper right denotes other basemap options.
